
Binning examples
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

./bayesian-binning.py -v -b -m data/data2.cfg
./bayesian-binning.py -m --which=1 data/data2.cfg

./bayesian-binning.py -v -b -m data/data8.cfg

./bayesian-binning.py -v -b -m --save=data/data8.result data/data8.cfg
./bayesian-binning.py -v -b -m --load=data/data8.result data/data8.cfg


Adaptive sampling examples
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

./adaptive-sampling.py -n 10 data/data12.cfg

./adaptive-sampling.py -n  10 -m --save=data/data12.result1 data/data12.cfg
./adaptive-sampling.py -n  90 -m --load=data/data12.result1 --save=data/data12.result2 data/data12.cfg
./adaptive-sampling.py -n 100 -m --load=data/data12.result2 --save=data/data12.result3 data/data12.cfg

./adaptive-sampling.py -m --load=data/data12.result3 data/data12.cfg
